<emphasis id="B938F752FF93FF86FB4CF93167C4A9CB" bold="true" box="[1184,1196,1718,1739]" pageId="2" pageNumber="47">7</emphasis>
, hypandrium and phallus, lateral view; 
<emphasis id="B938F752FF93FF86FEA9F952621DA9EA" bold="true" box="[325,373,1749,1770]" pageId="2" pageNumber="47">8–11</emphasis>
, paratype female. 
